<rgb=#66ffff>In Rohirrim</rgb>
<rgb=#FF7700>All things end, and sometimes the resolution brings great succor.</rgb>

<rgb=#66ffff>In Riddermark</rgb>
<rgb=#FF7700>All things end, and once resolved one can find they have been dumbfounded.</rgb>

<rgb=#66ffff>In Red Dawn</rgb>
<rgb=#FF7700>All things end, and when fire is involved all that remains is ash and ruin.</rgb>
